70817::$$$message_0649_0000_0000$$$::   I can't abandon Rider.[lr]::
70818::$$$message_0649_0000_0001$$$::I ignore the pain in my left arm and my eroding memories,[lr]::
70819::$$$message_0649_0000_0002$$$::draw the Azoth Blade, and dash at the black swordsman.::
70820::$$$message_0649_0001_0000$$$::My decision and movement are swift.[lr]::
70821::$$$message_0649_0001_0001$$$::My feet hurl me forward like a bomb blast,[lr]::
70822::$$$message_0649_0001_0002$$$::and my body flies through the air like a bullet.::
70823::$$$message_0649_0002_0000$$$::My blood flows backward. My senses flow backward. Poison flows backward.::
70824::$$$message_0649_0003_0000$$$::My left arm and my body are one.[lr]::
70825::$$$message_0649_0003_0001$$$::The novice Shirou Emiya transforms into a superman.::
70826::$$$message_0649_0004_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
70827::$$$message_0649_0004_0001$$$::One second feels like ten.[lr]::
70828::$$$message_0649_0004_0002$$$::   I can take her.[lr]::
70829::$$$message_0649_0004_0003$$$::Right now, I can fight against Saber, if I pay the broken Shirou Emiya as a price!::
70830::$$$message_0649_0005_0000$$$::"Run, Rider...!"[lr]::
70831::$$$message_0649_0005_0001$$$::I slash from the side at the two clashing, dark figures.[lr]::
70832::$$$message_0649_0005_0002$$$::"Ngh... Shirou!?"[lr]::
70833::$$$message_0649_0005_0003$$$::Rider kneels on the ground.[lr]::
70834::$$$message_0649_0005_0004$$$::"........."[lr]::
70835::$$$message_0649_0005_0005$$$::Saber reacts to me only with her eyes.::
70836::$$$message_0649_0006_0000$$$::   I got her.[lr]::
70837::$$$message_0649_0006_0001$$$::I bring the Azoth Blade down on Saber's defenseless left arm.::
70838::$$$message_0649_0007_0000$$$::"...Wha[line2]"[lr]::
70839::$$$message_0649_0007_0001$$$::It shatters.[lr]::
70840::$$$message_0649_0007_0002$$$::The dagger should have pierced her body, but it completely shattered as soon as it touched her.::
70841::$$$message_0649_0007_0003$$$::A lightspeed attack slashes me in response.[lr]::
70842::$$$message_0649_0007_0004$$$::I'm sliced open.[lr]::
70843::$$$message_0649_0007_0005$$$::Just as I intended, an arm goes tumbling to the ground.::
70844::$$$message_0649_0008_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
70845::$$$message_0649_0008_0001$$$::Rider jumps back, while Saber stands calmly.[lr]::
70846::$$$message_0649_0008_0002$$$::"Ah... Aaargh, gah......!"[lr]::
70847::$$$message_0649_0008_0003$$$::I kneel, trying desperately to stop the blood fountaining from my left shoulder.::
70848::$$$message_0649_0009_0000$$$::"Hah, ugh, guh, aaaaahhhhh!"[lr]::
70849::$$$message_0649_0009_0001$$$::I writhe in agony.[lr]::
70850::$$$message_0649_0009_0002$$$::"I did not fail to react. I simply did not need to, Shirou,"[lr]::
70851::$$$message_0649_0009_0003$$$::The black swordsman declares, in a stone-cold voice.[lr]::
70852::$$$message_0649_0009_0004$$$::I hear footsteps approaching.[lr]::
70853::$$$message_0649_0009_0005$$$::I'm helpless. She's be...behind me.::
70854::$$$message_0649_0010_0000$$$::"I've plucked out your fangs. ...Sakura does not say it, but she wants you to live. She would prefer that I render you harmless and bring you to her.[lr]::
70855::$$$message_0649_0010_0001$$$::But..."::
70856::$$$message_0649_0011_0000$$$::A sword bites into my back.[lr]::
70857::$$$message_0649_0011_0001$$$::The cold weight of death pushes in only a few centimeters, stopping just short of my heart.::
70858::$$$message_0649_0012_0000$$$::"...Choose. You can die here to my sword, or I can deliver you to Sakura, where you'll meet a fate worse than death. The choice is yours, Shirou."[lr]::
70859::$$$message_0649_0012_0001$$$::...My consciousness fades.[lr]::
70860::$$$message_0649_0012_0002$$$::I feel my blood leaving my body, and the weight of the blade in my back.::
70861::$$$message_0649_0013_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
70862::$$$message_0649_0013_0001$$$::...I don't know which option I chose.[lr]::
70863::$$$message_0649_0013_0002$$$::All I know is one thing: [lr]::
70864::$$$message_0649_0013_0003$$$::There's nothing I can do to save Sakura anymore.::

